author: pieber
msg: [KARAF-1468] Switched to the geronimo servlet spec version
The jetty one exports all packages in version 3.0 which is pretty...
well, let's say uncool... The geronimo versio on the other side exports
2.6 packages in 2.6 version and 3.0 packages in 3.0 which allows full
backward compatibility making the port to 3.0 ways less painful.
